  <div id="content"><p class="language"><a href="#">English</a> / <a href="../es/donate.htm">Español</a></p> 
    <h2>Donate</h2>
    <p>ARFWM provides funding to women and girls seeking abortion care who cannot afford it. Safe, legal, dignified abortions are an essential part of women's health care, but they are out of reach for many.  
      Nearly 100% of every donation is used to serve our clients. With your partnership, ARFWM can continue being a vital resource to the women who seek our support, to their families, and to our community. Our sisters, mothers, cousins, nieces, and daughters depend on people like you.</p>
    <h3>Payment Methods</h3>
    <p>1. <strong>By Credit Card through Razoo</strong><br /><br />
        <a href="http://www.razoo.com/story/Abortion-Rights-Fund-Of-Western-Massachusetts?referral_code=share"><img alt="Donate Now" border = "0" src="../images/donate-button.jpg" height="60" width="157">
    <p class="firstp">2. <strong>By Check</strong><br />
    Please make your check payable to The Abortion Rights Fund of Western MA:

    <p class="firstp">ARFWM<br />
      P.O. Box 2162<br />
      Amherst, MA 01004-2162</p>

    <p>ARFWM is a 501(c)(3) organization. Your donation is tax-deductible to the
      full extent of the law.</p>

    <hr />
  </div>
  <div id="rightcolumn">
      <p class="quote">We are a community-based, all-volunteer organization dedicated to overcoming the economic barriers to abortion care. Our committed volunteers give their time and individual donors give their financial support because they know that without money, a right is meaningless. </p>
